* {{flagcountry|Somalia}}：索馬里共接收到450枝步槍，用以處理叛亂。<ref name="Haber7">{{Cite web |url=http://ekonomi.haber7.com/ekonomi/haber/2460971-sinirlari-asti-dunya-pesine-dustu |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-12-25 |archive-date=2017-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171031122419/http://ekonomi.haber7.com/ekonomi/haber/2460971-sinirlari-asti-dunya-pesine-dustu |dead-url=no }}</ref>

